      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This car has plenty of personality and is ready for a dedicated owner to restore it to its former glory! While it currently needs some significant mechanical and cosmetic TLC, it offers a fantastic foundation for anyone who loves a hands-on automotive challenge. Grab this opportunity to breathe new life into a vehicle with great potential!",
