    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable for daily commutes, and honestly just a joy to drive! I've taken great care of it over the years, and it\u2019s officially ready to hit the road with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels great, this is the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 28900.0,
