      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously cared-for 2017 Porsche Macan S finished in Volcano Grey Metallic with a matching Agate Grey leather interior. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a daily commuter and a performance machine. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well, typical for a car of this age. The 19-inch Macan Design wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in Michelin tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a testament to Porsche quality; the leather seats show only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracking. All interior electronics, including the heated seats, navigation, and multi-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the 3.0L Twin-Turbo V6 runs flawlessly, with no leaks or warning lights. I have a complete binder of service records, including the most recent 40,000-mile major service which included a spark plug change and brake fluid flush. This Macan S offers a tight, responsive drive and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
